  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>To evaluate the efficacity (non-inferiority) in terms of response between patients using mandibular advancement devices ONIRIS® and patient using devices produced in a laboratoryTALI after 2 months of use.</measure>
    <time_frame>2 monthes of use</time_frame>
    <description>The response to the treatment is defined as:
complete patient response: AHI per hour of sleep &lt; 10 or
partial patient response: AHI per hour of sleep reduced by 50% at visit M2 compared to baseline</description>
  </primary_outcome>
